name: RandomAnything
0:
”Alexa, tell Random Anything to give me three numbers.”
”What should I eat today?”
”Tell me something.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: random anything
des:
Don't know what to eat? Let Random Anything help you decide!
It supports: food, restaurant, word, name, number, car brand, country name.
Here are some examples for what you can ask:
"What should I eat today?"
"Tell me something."
"Give me three numbers."
"Tell me a car brand."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
